{
  "stem": "3638.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was they tolerate us, because the school was open on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was from-- from Monday to Saturday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- but the teachers tolerate us because we didn't come on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went to synagogue.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I used to have a few non-Jewish friends, which I always used to go to them and they told me what was-- what-- what we learned on Sunday-- on Saturday-- and I had to catch up.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was every week.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, only to the last two years, were there-- between '35, '36 were the anti-semitism was growing in Poland due to the Hitler in the moment.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But up till then, I didn't feel anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I didn't notice nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- it was a very short distance from home to the school, walking distance.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there-- there used to be anti-semitism, and particularly my father felt it in the trade, because there was one minister, he used to say-- he got out and he said, his word was you should not hate the Jews.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But what you should do, you should boycott them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In other words, don't buy off them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, you understand what I mean?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's what we felt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, don't hate them, don't prosecute them, just boycott them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that went right through the community.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we did not-- could do so much trade as of course before those-- before those years.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we still survive, because the competition-- they still have to come, because we were the cheapest or something like that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it changed sudden.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Up to '39, we didn't-- hardship, we did not feel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was plenty to eat, and we sleeped and everyth-- there's no problem.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the change suddenly, 1939, when the German move into Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
